SCORECANDS runs server-side Mercury-style proximity scoring of every available candidate against a single job's profile. Params: PARAM.salary_mid (midpoint of job's salary range), PARAM.exp_target, PARAM.remote_pref. Weights: desired_salary proximity 3, experience proximity 2, remote match 2 (max score 7, normalized to 0-1). Output pipe-delimited with score first. Used by the employer's "Top Candidates" view for a specific job. Server-side counterpart to SCOREJOBS.
